    "title": "Zawadi ya Vifaa",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "zawadi ya vifaa",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kwenye Agano la Kale, watu mara nyingi waliamini kwamba watu wema daima wangekuwa matajiri. Waliona hekima kutoka kwa vitabu kama Mithali kama kanuni ya ulimwengu. Watu wengine bado wanaamini hivi leo. Tatizo moja na imani hii ni kwamba inaweza kusababisha watu kuhisi hatia au kulaumu wengine wanaposhindwa kufanikiwa. Inaweza pia kusababisha uvivu kwa wale wanaofanikiwa.</p><p>Mateso ya mzee Ayubu yanatoa mfano. Marafiki zake walikubali mtazamo wa kitheolojia wa jadi uliosema matatizo ya Ayubu yalikuwa ushahidi dhidi yake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:5\">19:5</a>). Walidai mateso yake yalikuwa adhabu kwa dhambi zake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:7-Job4:9\">4:7–9</a>). Waliamini adhabu ya Ayubu ilikuwa pengine chini ya alivyostahili (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:6\">11:6</a>). Hata hivyo, uchambuzi wa Mungu wa maisha ya Ayubu ulithibitisha kuwa wazo hili halikuwa sahihi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:7-Job42:8\">42:7–8</a>). Mungu alithibitisha uhusiano wake maalum na Ayubu na kurejesha sifa njema ya Ayubu kama mtumishi wake.</p><p>Ustawi wa kimwili haupingani kila mara na baraka za kiroho. Hata hivyo, tunapoona baraka kama faida ya kimwili, &quot;shida za maisha haya, udanganyifu wa mali, na tamaa ya vitu vingine&quot; mara nyingi hutukatisha tamaa kutoka kwa baraka za kiroho (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:19\">Marko 4:19</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:25\">Luka 6:25</a>). Tunaweza kwa urahisi kuwa na tamaa, wivu, na tamaa mbaya. Thamani yetu binafsi inaweza kutegemea kile tunachomiliki, hata kama bado tunadaiwa pesa juu yake. Mtazamo huu si wa Kikristo bali unaakisi njia ya kufikiri ya kidunia (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:15-1John2:17\">1 Yohana 2:15–17</a>).</p><p>Katika mateso yake, Ayubu alibadilika kutoka kulalamika hadi kuonyesha unyenyekevu. Alitambua nguvu na haki za Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:4-Job40:5\">Ayubu 40:4–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:2-Job42:6\">42:2–6</a>). Sisi pia tunaweza kuona matatizo kama fursa za kukua kiroho (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:2-Jas1:4\">Yakobo 1:2–4</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:2\">Mwanzo 13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:23\">1 Wafalme 10:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:7-Job4:9\">Ayubu 4:7–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:6\">11:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:5\">19:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:16-Ps49:20\">Zaburi 49:16–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:1-Ps73:28\">73:1–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:20\">Mithali 14:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:11\">18:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:11\">28:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:10-Eccl5:20\">Mhubiri 5:10–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:11\">Yeremia 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:18\">Sefania 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:57\">Mathayo 27:57</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:19\">Marko 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:17-Mark10:25\">10:17–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:24-Luke6:25\">Luka 6:24–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:10-Luke16:31\">16:10–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1 Timotheo 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:2-Jas1:4\">Yakobo 1:2–4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:9\">9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:1\">5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:16\">1 Yohana 2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:2\">3 Yohana 1:2</a></p>",
